<br>
&quot;Paying newbs to drown themselves.&quot;<br>
<br>
It seems he would give newbs 20pp to drown themselves in the lake. He said it made him laugh. I told him he was one sick dude. He's still one of my best friends in game LOL. <br>
<br>
And THAT is the funniest thing I remember seeing in EQ for a long, long time. Newbies choking to death. For 20pp. *chuckle*<br>
<br>
Baervon<br>
