<br>
After getting bristlebanes bundle I went back to my old newbie grounds and started summoning, beer, cake, and toys. Then i said, what's more fun then drunk newbies? Flying drunk newbies. So I started dropping rings of flight. Then eventaully anything that had a right click to it. After warming the newbies up for maybe a half hour on fun trinkets I started to drop the trans rods. At that point they were so used to picking them up and clicking the toys, they didn't look at what they were. Well, at least they skipped the hang overs.<br>
<br>
